  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK615">
<l>iṉpam viḻaiyāṉviṉaiviḻaivāṉ ṟaṉkēḷir </l>
<l> tuṉpan tuṭaittūṉṟun tūṇ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He who desires not pleasure, but desires labour, will be a pillar to sustain his relations, wiping away their sorrows.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
